description: This common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 33, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 99, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Nine Lives for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [99 Votes, Common]
